This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques to analyze tweets related to the Cambridge Analytica scandal. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also deals with information privacy, which falls under the categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper also deals with data collection and risks, which falls under the category of cs.SD (Software Engineering).
